Scala is a fantastic language, but my heart seems to resist due to things like this (slide 27/42):<p><pre><code>  implicit class RichSeq[A, C[A] <: Seq[A]](underlying: C[A]{
    def cycle: Iterator[A] = {
      lazy val circular: Stream[A] = underlying.toStream #::: circular
      circular.iterator
    }
  }</code></pre>
